export const homeObjOne = {
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,

    headline: 'Get your DIY and repair services Fix it',
    description:
      'Need a trusted handyman in your neighborhood? Discover the DIY home service with FeliX.',
    buttonLabel: '',
    imgStart: '',
    img: 'images/gold_hammer-removebg-preview.png',
    alt: 'FeliX logo'
  };
  
  export const homeObjTwo = {
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,

      'Once your DIY ad is published, you will receive responses for the completion of your work. It is up to you to discuss with the jobbers to find an agreement and carry out your DIY work at home.',
    buttonLabel: '',
    imgStart: '',
    img: 'images/undraw_accept_tasks_po1c.svg',
    alt: ''
  };
  
  export const homeObjThree = {
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'EASY SETUP',
    headline: 'Offer your DIY services and get yourself the job',
    description:
      "Get everything set up and ready in under 3 minutes. All you need to do is add your information and you're ready to go.",
    buttonLabel: '',
    imgStart: 'start',
    img: 'images/undraw_coffee_break_h3uu.svg',
    alt: 'jobber'
  };
